0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-13T18:51:05.693484556Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aM1VsZGlRVmxsVmtadFNsOVdVM1ZFUmtSTFVWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aM1VsZGlRVmxsVmtadFNsOVdVM1ZFUmtSTFVWRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a115e46d915:0xf52cb27f5b311a25"},{"name":"places/ChIJFdlGXhFawokRJRoxW3-yLPU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25neVdIYzRjbWN5TjI1YWR6QkNVVlJaU1dKWlpFRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 weeks ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I have been going to City Dental since 2021. Great experience with them. I highly recommend Dr. Atsen. He is patient, meticulous and very detailed with his explanations and work. The office is clean and modern. The staff are helpful and easy to deal with.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I have been going to City Dental since 2021. Great experience with them. I highly recommend Dr. Atsen. He is patient, meticulous and very detailed with his explanations and work. The office is clean and modern. The staff are helpful and easy to deal with.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Yaron Ronnie Solomon","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102466087708719081801/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU04SBPQ4D-v-1TO3Yo8Ijohej5QXPwf1vSrNjlR24-LxXzJwkt=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-22T20:31:55.719148401Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25neVdIYzRjbWN5TjI1YWR6QkNVVlJaU1dKWlpFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25neVdIYzRjbWN5TjI1YWR6QkNVVlJaU1dKWlpFRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a115e46d915:0xf52cb27f5b311a25"},{"name":"places/ChIJFdlGXhFawokRJRoxW3-yLPU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GcWNtYzBZbGRqUm5nNE5YUTRSVkZKVjJodVFVRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I had my first visit today for a cleaning. I had a great experience all around. They called me back as soon as I finished the paperwork, before my scheduled appointment time. The receptionist, tech, hygienist, and dentist were all polite, professional, concise, and efficient. I gladly scheduled follow-up appointments and will be going here for the foreseeable future.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I had my first visit today for a cleaning. I had a great experience all around. They called me back as soon as I finished the paperwork, before my scheduled appointment time. The receptionist, tech, hygienist, and dentist were all polite, professional, concise, and efficient. I gladly scheduled follow-up appointments and will be going here for the foreseeable future.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Benji Birchfield","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114965961245590751058/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUZeED4fWuVRHzIa8fcacmRMrBI2NSxY9CANKJzKgFidRWAeAV=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2026-01-12T22:36:57.955265693Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GcWNtYzBZbGRqUm5nNE5YUTRSVkZKVjJodVFVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GcWNtYzBZbGRqUm5nNE5YUTRSVkZKVjJodVFVRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a115e46d915:0xf52cb27f5b311a25"},{"name":"places/ChIJFdlGXhFawokRJRoxW3-yLPU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkSlJFUmtSVVZTVlVVMlIwWm5ZVmxKVUZGcVpWRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"4 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"First time I went there. Everyone from the receptionist to the dentist and everyone in between was absolutely wonderful. The dentist has a lovely, gentle, but firm touch. He explained everything and gave me options. He submitted my needed claims, even though my insurance usually turns some of the items down. Just an all over great experience!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"First time I went there. Everyone from the receptionist to the dentist and everyone in between was absolutely wonderful. The dentist has a lovely, gentle, but firm touch. He explained everything and gave me options. He submitted my needed claims, even though my insurance usually turns some of the items down. Just an all over great experience!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Gill Jagroop","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112571107405271058739/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoWoasayStZsaYfpPPcdFbKR6a9Stx4bKtSQs9kmtzMsRSZg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-09-24T23:43:17.180592240Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkSlJFUmtSVVZTVlVVMlIwWm5ZVmxKVUZGcVpWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkSlJFUmtSVVZTVlVVMlIwWm5ZVmxKVUZGcVpWRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c25a115e46d915:0xf52cb27f5b311a25"},{"name":"places/ChIJFdlGXhFawokRJRoxW3-yLPU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tFdFZIZzBMVUZoU2xWdGMySnVkVEo2Ympac2NVRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I was very happy with my visit from start (making appointment) to finish- meeting with dentist- Dr Kim- he was very thorough with explaining my issues- in between- the assistant - very professional- and hygienist - gentle yet thorough- I will definitely return in 6 months for my next cleaning","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I was very happy with my visit from start (making appointment) to finish- meeting with dentist- Dr Kim- he was very thorough with explaining my issues- in between- the assistant - very professional- and hygienist - gentle yet thorough- I will definitely return in 6 months for my next cleaning","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttr